(21, 153, 'stathis', 'stathis@spill.com.gr', '', '94.66.140.11', '2010-08-04 03:58:12', '2010-08-04 08:58:12', 'Hi JB! Great job on the illo. \nComing form Greece, things are very dodgy over here indeed.. Pentions are just one of a multitude of problems.. I find however that\npracticing the art of illustration always takes my mind of things..\nTake care!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
