(26, 268, 'Anne', 'anne.moore@candlewick.com', 'http://www.candlewick.com', '75.147.35.157', '2011-01-06 17:13:50', '2011-01-06 22:13:50', 'You. I sympathize with YOU ~ you are soooooo talented!\nVery interesting question posed though...reminds me of tension/issues in Rembrandt''s RETURN OF THE PRODIGAL SON where the Father is the sympathetic one, although his size is larger &amp; standing over his son ~ but there is no domination... just tenderness &amp; strength from the power of love. \nhttp://www.wga.hu/support/viewer/z.html', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
