(81, 2, '2010-04-07 18:08:56', '2010-04-07 23:08:56', 'In response to <a href="http://www.smartplanet.com/technology/blog/thinking-tech/how-to-protect-your-copyrighted-images-on-the-web/3684/#comments" target="_blank">this little discussion</a> you may have caught wind of...\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/thisiscopyrightwatermark1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-83" title="thisiscopyrightwatermark" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/thisiscopyrightwatermark1.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="234" /></a>\n<p style="text-align:center;">"Just put a watermark across <em>part </em>of the image."</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#ff0000;">"But boss, it kind of dilutes the product,I dont think we are effectively selling the message now."</span></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"></p>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#ff0000;">\n</span></p>', 'WATERMARK YOUR WORK! (watermark my work?)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'watermark-your-work-watermark-my-work', '', '', '2010-04-07 18:08:56', '2010-04-07 23:08:56', '', 0, 'http://seejbdraw.wordpress.com/?p=81', 0, 'post', '', 1),
