(298, 2, '2011-02-10 09:07:49', '2011-02-10 14:07:49', '"Absurdist Logic" has a double page spread in the latest 3x3 Annual. Wow. A sincere thank you, Charles.\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/333.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-299" title="333" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/333.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="608" /></a>\n<p style="text-align:center;"><span style="color:#888888;"><em>*editors note: No I do not paint my fingernails</em></span></p>', '3x3 Annual #7', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '3x3-annual-7', '', '', '2011-02-10 09:07:49', '2011-02-10 14:07:49', '', 0, 'http://seejbdraw.wordpress.com/?p=298', 0, 'post', '', 0),
