(306, 2, '2011-02-27 09:41:05', '2011-02-27 14:41:05', '<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/oscar1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-307" title="oscar1" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/oscar1.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="758" /></a>\n\nIt''s the big night, right? Sure, why not!\n\nI had the privilege of illustrating the cover of the Sunday Calendar section for The Los Angeles Times, honoring Hollywood''s biggest night.  Many thanks to the design team to include me alongside the other six artists for this fun series of images.\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/oscar1.jpg"><a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/oscar21.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-309" title="oscar2" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/oscar21.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="440" /></a>\n</a>\n\nAbout the art: "I wanted to have a little tongue-in-cheek fun with the most important part of the Oscars, that is, winning. Everyone always thanks a list of people, but what you don''t see is the other side of the page..."\n\n<a href="http://tinyurl.com/64kuexa">More info here</a>', 'OSCAR SUNDAY, READ ALL ABOUT IT!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oscar-sunday-read-all-about-it', '', '', '2011-02-27 09:41:05', '2011-02-27 14:41:05', '', 0, 'http://seejbdraw.wordpress.com/?p=306', 0, 'post', '', 1),
