(507, 2, '2011-09-10 15:38:56', '2011-09-10 20:38:56', 'I love bow ties so when the opportunity to illustrate a series of images for a tie maker came along I jumped at the chance. I am extremely excited to finally be able to share the results of my collaboration with the lovely folks over at <strong>Pierrepont Hicks</strong>. They make extraordinary ties and have put together a unique approach to their Fall/Winter 2011 look book. Had way too much fun working with this concept. Enjoy!\n\nI will be selling 8"x10" archival prints of these images as well. <a href="http://seejbdraw.com/purchase.html">Go here to purchase</a>\n\n<a href="http://pierreponthicks.com/main.aspx">Visit Pierrepont Hicks</a>\n\n<a href="http://seejbdraw.com/PPHICKS_2011_web.pdf">View the pdf look book</a>\n\nSo many images to share so lets get to it:\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/picture-61.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-509" title="Picture 6" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/picture-61.png" alt="" width="450" height="262" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/buck.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-510" title="buck" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/buck.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="558" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/buzz.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-511" title="buzz" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/buzz.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="558" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/frog.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-512" title="frog" src="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/frog.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="558" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/jonathanbartlett/wp-content/uploads/2011/